How to run

- Dependencies: Python 3.8+, Flask.
- Install: pip install flask
- Run: python app.py
- Open your browser at http://localhost:5000
- Use arrow keys to slide tiles. New tiles spawn after valid moves. The score and highest tile are shown; game ends when no moves are possible. Use “New Game” to start over.

